title: VersaEmerge Discography - All Three EPs
description:
***************************************************

This is a collection of every EP VersaEmerge has released to date, including the Cities Built On Sand EP with VersaEmerge's previous vocalist Spencer Pearson.

Happy listening. And please seed so others can enjoy as well! And if you can manage to support the band in any way, by donating, going to their shows, or buying their albums, this is always preferred!
